# C-Flow-4 Git Strategy: Root-level Management

# --- Node.js & Dependencies ---
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Frontend (Vite/React) ---
frontend/dist/
frontend/build/
.vite/

# --- Environment Files (CRITICAL) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Databases ---
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
backend/*.db
backend/*.sqlite

# --- Logs ---
logs/
*.log
backend/logs/

# --- OS & Editor Files ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
Thumbs.db
